r />\n佢樣靚身材正 脾氣又好 仲要勁有愛心 比隻狗咬到留疤都無棄養 其實愛狗既人都未必會咁做 因為唔多唔少都會留有1d心理暗影 驚隻狗會再咬自己 同埋睇得出佢人緣幾好 睇佢ig見到同好多人既合照同互動某程度上我自己都係因為佢有愛心所以先開始留意同鍾意佢 因為好難搵到一個內在美同外在美都靚既藝人 <br />\n我越講越有痴漢feel 自己都驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0151ff2eb572b9b28acc8495019546573bc1c0fc","tid":424874,"uid":294,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://202.125.90.20/cnt/entertainment/20130405/photo/0405-00470-060b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F202.125.90.20%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20130405%2Fphoto%2F0405-00470-060b3.jpg&h=3baac2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2015/01/15/1/15829ce94382a3091f052b3b12fd30d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2015%2F01%2F15%2F1%2F15829ce94382a3091f052b3b12fd30d5.jpg&h=8ad3c423&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i817.photobucket.com/albums/zz98/gundamzetainhkg/08-09-2010/5th/09-08_20-03-33_HighDefinitionJade_09-0822-00-31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi817.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fzz98%2Fgundamzetainhkg%2F08-09-2010%2F5th%2F09-08_20-03-33_HighDefinitionJade_09-0822-00-31.jpg&h=534c6cb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb5c45ca57bc3d30f55aa038b5fc4995d1767aeb","tid":424874,"uid":105498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T22:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾靚都好咪臭係食煙既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有幅坐泳池邊食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b20050392cd955c486a19fee8ca0723b0816239","tid":424874,"uid":7638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T22:22:37.000Z","msg":"對我黎講佢本身都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82fb74c9c967376c8a64b2be2dbdca77868faa1","tid":424874,"uid":125423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-