\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2d78de2afd6db2399fcbe7790520e8bb3ae2cb61","tid":424874,"uid":61279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:33:02.000Z","msg":"CCTVB 首席眼鏡娘，<br />\n之後就係黃智雯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299d788dbfb92683e5ce27e6036e8bb1f1f82618","tid":424874,"uid":78047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估唔到佢由四葉草個時變到而家咁正"},{"pid":"44e966a5a853920d7163714c8cbe876c8b484b48","tid":424874,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>表哥以前某套劇的眼鏡OL Look真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打有留底</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/000125_6e557ee2a98291ab50a43908916016fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F000125_6e557ee2a98291ab50a43908916016fb.jpg&h=e989db21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/000126_6e557ee2a98291ab50a43908916016fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F000126_6e557ee2a98291ab50a43908916016fb.jpg&h=0ac06c83&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n情越雙白線<br />\n讀書果陣就嫁咗比曹永廉大埋肚.但曹永廉al入唔倒u,走咗去揸的士,跟住表哥出黎做野耐咗覺得同守門員越黎越大距離,加上煎pan係咁對佢示好(但其實係煎pan利用表哥幫自己D不法勾當簽名),有一次出差仲好似一齊扑咗(好似無明示,但畫面有暗示),但無耐之後表哥偷聽倒煎pan同人講係利用自己,又比煎pan發現,所以搞到捉走咗佢定唔知搞到佢跌咗落樓梯重傷,最後好似<span style=\"color: green;\">大團圓</span>結局"},{"pid":"f0dda0e0